ath\n   - Otherwise serves the UI assets\n\n4. **internal/servers/controller/handler_noui.go (lines 29-30)**\n   - Same passthrough logic for non-UI builds\n\n5. **internal/servers/controller/handler_ui_test.go (line 44)**\n   - Sets the config field for testing passthrough functionality\n\n## Behavior\n\nWhen the flag/env var is set, the webserver serves files from the specified directory at the root path `/`. If not set, it returns `404 Not Found` for UI requests.\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_09b8b2b51ffemZ1aPTUry58Fin","model":{"modelID":"unsloth/GLM-4.7-Flash-GGUF:UD-Q4_K_XL","providerID":"local"},"truncated":false},"title":"Find passthrough flag details","time":{"start":1784096806075,"end":1784097154526}},"id":"prt_f64748c480018R5fxKX2tKDF7O","sessionID":"ses_09b8cf439ffe6rZam42YqSaiFx","messageID":"msg_f64747518001uXLunGLzXUhssm"}}
